title: David Icke - The Robots Rebellion (1994)
description:
Many people critisize David Icke for his reptilian theories, but in this 1994 video he does not mention reptiles even once. Everything in this talk is verifiable, it is Icke&#039;s best lecture IMO, a lecture of sheer genius. Listen to what he says about John F Kerry and remember he is saying it in 1994 not 2004.

Its not really a case of "David Icke, was he right?" but rather "David Icke was right, period."
